cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "LitGraph"
abstract: >
  LitGraph is an open-source agentic RAG system for democratizing access
  to public-domain literary classics. It generates personalized study guides
  and answers questions grounded in source text evidence, using LangGraph,
  ChromaDB, and a custom MCP server backed by the Project Gutenberg corpus.
